1. What is screen scraping?
The term is about all options of reading texts on computer monitors.

2. Who uses screen scraping?
Search Engines (e.g Google)
Web Services
Remixing (Mashups)
..

3. Are we allowed to show screen shots of arbitrary web sites on our own web site?
you need to take care of the copyrights,
if you develop a program that makes screen scrapping for the client site possibly it is okay
some providers explicitly forbid screen scrapping on there web pages

